  <title class="- topic/title ">How Dynamic Offers Work</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Dynamic offers use your dynamic page
	 technology to pass values to the offer. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
    <p class="- topic/p ">The offer is executed after you render the page. An
		invisible iframe gathers the data, copies it out of the frame and inserts in on
		the page, loading your passed values. 
	 </p>
